external.title: Schedule | PowerShell + DevOps Global Summit

record.text:
In my opinion, #PSHSummit 2026 boasts the best speaker lineup and schedule since 2019. There is no better place to learn PowerShel & DevOps-related content in North America than at this event.

Tickets are on sale now, and you'd be doing your career a disservice by not attending.
